condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I.A.1PA, Schedule, Section I.A.1 | Description :The Borrower shall cause the PIE to,and PIE shall carry out the Project in accordance with the Project Operational Manual and shall not amend, suspend, abrogate,repeal or waive any provision of said Manual without the prior written approval of the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I.A.2PA, Schedule, Section I.A.2 | Description :The Borrower shall cause the PIE to,and PIE shall maintain the PIU until the completion of the Project, and shall ensure that the PIU is adequately staffed bypersonnel with qualifications and under terms of reference and functions at all times in accordance with procedures necessary andappropriate for the carrying out of the Project, and satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I.A.3PA, Schedule, Section I.A.3 | Description :During the implementation of theProject, the Borrower shall cause the PIE to, and PIE shall retain the services of a construction management company satisfactoryto the Bank until the Bank’s assessment has determined that the PIE has the capacity to take over such a responsibilityindependently. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I.B.1 | Description :To facilitate the carrying out of the Project, the Borrower shallmake the proceeds of the Loan available to the PIE under a subsidiary agreement between the Borrower and the PIE, under terms andconditions acceptable to the Bank (“Subsidiary Agreement”). | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I.B.2 | Description :The Borrower shall exercise its rights under the SubsidiaryAgreement in such manner as to protect the interests of the Borrower and the Bank and to accomplish the purposes of the Loan.Except as the Bank shall otherwise agree, the Borrower shall not assign, amend, abrogate or waive the Subsidiary Agreement or anyof its provisions. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I.D.1PA, Schedule, Section I.C.1 | Description :The Borrower shall cause the PIE to,and PIE shall carry out the Project in accordance with the provisions of the EIAF, site-specific EIAs and EMPs, RPF and RAP, andshall not assign, amend, abrogate or waive the EIA, EMP, RPF and/or RAP or any provision thereof, without prior approval of theBank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
